Package de.rwth.i2.attestor.semantics.jimpleSemantics.jimple.statements Description

This package containsSubsumingState the semantics of jimple statements on jimpleExecutables. They all implement the interface Statement.
Classes used to handle invokes can be found in the sub-package invoke
